Metadata: Oregon Commercial Fisheries (Volume 7, No. 2 and Volume 8, No. 1 and No. 2, May, September, and November 1976)
Oregon State University Extension Service, Sea Grant Marine Advisory Program
Three newsletter issues in one entry for 1976.

Topics in these newsletter issues include: The 200-mile fisheries zone; troll-salmon regulations; marine weather coverage; battery chargers on boats; Loran-C charts; salmon in the future; 1976 tax reform act; capital construction fund; razor clamming; navigation; radio direction finding (RDF); bathymetric charts.
